data.caption: Announcement under Regulation 30 (LODR)-Earnings Call Transcript
data.news_body: Pursuant to Regulation 30 of the SEBI (LODR) Regulations 2015 we are enclosing herewith the transcript of the Earning Call on Financial Results of the Company for the quarter ended December 31 2025.

data.caption: Announcement under Regulation 30 (LODR)-Analyst / Investor Meet - Outcome
data.news_body: Pursuant to Regulation 30 of the SEBI (LODR) Regulations 2015 we wish to inform you that the audio call recording of earnings conference call on the Financial Results of the Tata Motors Limited (formerly TML Commercial Vehicles Limited) for the third quarter and nine months ended December 31 2025 held on January 29 2026 is available on the Companys website.

data.caption: Announcement under Regulation 30 (LODR)-Investor Presentation
data.news_body: Pursuant to Regulation 30 of the SEBI Listing Regulations 2015 we hereby enclose the revised investor presentation to be made to the Analysts/ Investors on the Financial Results for the third quarter and nine months ended  December 31 2025

data.caption: Announcement under Regulation 30 (LODR)-Investor Presentation
data.news_body: Pursuant to Regulation 30 of SEBI LODR Regulations 2015 we are hereby enclosing the investor presentation on the financial results for the quarter and nine months ended December 31 2025.

data.caption: Intimation Of Outcome Of Board Meeting Under Regulations 33 And 52 Of The SEBI (Listing Obligations And Disclosure Requirements) Regulations 2015
data.news_body: Pursuant to Regulation 33 and 52 and other applicable Regulations of the SEBI LODR Regulations 2015 we are enclosing herewith the financial results for the quarter and nine months ended December 31 2025.

data.caption: Announcement under Regulation 30 (LODR)-Earnings Call Transcript
data.news_body: Pursuant to Regulation 30 of the SEBI (LODR) Regulations 2015 we are enclosing herewith the transcript of the Earning call conducted on November 13 2025 on the Financial Results of the Company.

data.caption: Announcement under Regulation 30 (LODR)-Analyst / Investor Meet - Outcome
data.news_body: Pursuant to Regulation 30 of the SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulations 2015 we wish to inform you that the audio call recording of earnings conference call on the Financial Results of the Tata Motors Limited (formerly TML Commercial Vehicles Limited) for the second quarter and half year ended September 30 2025 held on November 13 2025 is available on the Companys website.

data.caption: Announcement under Regulation 30 (LODR)-Investor Presentation
data.news_body: Pursuant to Regulation 30 of the SEBI (LODR) Regulations 2015 we are enclosing herewith the investor presentation to be made to the Analyst/Investor on the Financial Results of Tata Motors Limited(formerly TML Commercial Vehicles Limited) for the second quarter and half year ended September 30 2025.

data.caption: The Board Of Directors At Is Meeting Held On November 13 2025 Approved The Financial Results For The Second Quarter And Half Year Ended September 30 2025
data.news_body: Pursuant to Regulations 33 and 52 of the SEBI LODR 2015 please find enclosed herewith the Audited Standalone Financial Results along with Auditors Report thereon and the Unaudited Consolidated Financial Results along with the Limited Review Report thereon for the second quarter and half year ended September 30 2025
